Build a production-quality local web application: a Kubernetes/OpenShift log explorer designed for stable, predictable debugging using a snapshot + refresh model (NO live streaming by default).

The goal is to eliminate UI chaos while preserving full log fidelity, ordering, and context.

---

🧱 Tech Stack (STRICT)

Frontend

- React (Vite)
- TypeScript
- TailwindCSS
- shadcn/ui
- Zustand (state management)
- react-window (virtualized rendering)

Backend

- Node.js (LTS)
- Express
- child_process.spawn (for "oc logs")
- NO WebSockets required (polling/refresh only)
- NO external logging systems

---

🎯 CORE PRODUCT PRINCIPLE

This tool is:

