---

🟡 New Logs Indicator (CRITICAL UX)

When new logs arrive (manual or auto refresh):

Show:

+37 new logs
[Show]

Rules:

- Indicator is visible but non-intrusive
- Clicking “Show” scrolls to latest logs
- Until clicked → user position remains unchanged

